{"tid":877483,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"葡超勁旅簽入一名香港球員","createTime":"2018-10-26T11:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T05:09:50.000Z","uid":190524,"like":287,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"3fc44b72d8802c34d9e1857ae31de8ebfaca8269","tid":877483,"uid":190524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T11:24:51.000Z","msg":"~標準流浪U15隊長加盟葡萄牙士砵亭~<br />\n流浪U15球員吳以琛Sun,剛剛簽約葡萄牙士砵亭，<br />\n吳以琛是標準流浪U15隊長，現年15歲，身高1米94，司職守門員，也是英華書院校隊，因為今季有師傅盧國華指點，進步神速，發揮表現出色，因而獲國外球會士砵亭睇中簽約。<br />\n葡萄牙及中國國內報章都有報導這單新聞，國內報章更以中國姚明，中國保方形容Sun。而且是中國往葡萄牙發展第一人。<br />\n標準流浪會方在此祝以琛出外發展順利，繼續有進步，有好發揮，為港爭光。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sporting/detalhe/yee-sun-ng-contratado\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.record.pt%2Ffutebol%2Ffutebol-nacional%2Fliga-nos%2Fsporting%2Fdetalhe%2Fyee-sun-ng-contratado&d=o9esMXOXSZYuEuFvbKfKYp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=f7fd41b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sporting/detalhe/yee-sun-ng-contratado</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.marca.com/futbol/liga-portuguesa/2018/10/18/5bc88219e5fdea8f488b4685.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marca.com%2Ffutbol%2Fliga-portuguesa%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F5bc88219e5fdea8f488b4685.html&d=o9esMXOXSZYuEuFvbKfKYp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=37f364a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.marca.com/futbol/liga-portuguesa/2018/10/18/5bc88219e5fdea8f488b4685.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://xw.qq.com/sport/20181018014168/SPO2018101801416800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fxw.qq.com%2Fsport%2F20181018014168%2FSPO2018101801416800&d=o9esMXOXSZYuEuFvbKfKYp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=94ca3116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://xw.qq.com/sport/20181018014168/SPO2018101801416800</a>"},{"pid":"2bc5b519479a78906581a833cf2ec889c33d376b","tid":877483,"uid":60658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0